room_title: Escape room "Ozark Mafia" by Escape Plan in Columbia (MO)
review: The new Ozark Mafia room was great! Loved it! Will definitely be back for the other rooms!

room_title: Escape room "Ozark Mafia" by Escape Plan in Columbia (MO)
review: We had a great time doing the Ozark Room this weekend. Staff was extremely friendly! We look forward to going back and trying another room.

room_title: Escape room "Ozark Mafia" by Escape Plan in Columbia (MO)
review: We had so much fun escaping our room! It was difficult but not impossible. The Ozark Mafia room had a fun story and was well managed. The guys were really friendly and helpful. Our group had a great time. Fun group activity and would definitely go again!

room_title: Escape room "Ozark Mafia" by Escape Plan in Columbia (MO)
review: First time here and tried the Ozark Mafia room! Great set up and just enough of a challenge! Dan was awesome in setting this room up and taking care of us! Highly recommended!

room_title: Escape room "Ozark Mafia" by Escape Plan in Columbia (MO)
review: Ozark Mafia was a great room to try. Staff was very friendly and the place was clean and well put together. Great activity for groups.
